    "In addition to GPU, the development of new hardware, especially surface scanning, line scanning, active/passive laser, and femtosecond lidar, also provides new opportunities for point cloud data registration of Lidar (Zhang et al., 2017).",
    "In addition to the hardware mentioned above, software is also an important factor affecting the registration effect of deep point cloud.",
